1- JSON request para manage_instance function (POST)

{
  "region": "us-east-1",
  "instances": [
    {
      "id_instance": "i-0123456789abcdef0",
      "action": "terminate"
    },
    {
      "id_instance": "i-0abcdef1234567890",
      "action": "stop"
    }
  ]
}
